window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Legendary science fiction author Orson Scott Card calls Brandon Sanderson a writer to watch. </p> <p>Once the godlike rulers of the capital of Arelon, the inhabitans of Elantris have been imprisoned within themselves, unable to die after the city's magic failed years ago. But when a new prince falls victim to the curse, he refuses to accept his fate. </p>"; 
